Global Anhydrous Ferric Chloride Market Insights
Anhydrous Ferric Chloride Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.10 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Anhydrous Ferric Chloride Market Overview
The global Anhydrous Ferric Chloride market has experienced significant growth over recent years and is expected to continue expanding at a steady rate. With a market value of USD 1.2 billion in 2023, the market is projected to reach USD 1.9 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5%. The increasing demand for water treatment, waste treatment, and metal surface treatment applications is fueling this growth. Anhydrous Ferric Chloride is widely used in various industries due to its versatility and effectiveness in industrial processes, leading to an increase in market demand.

